{
  "stem": "4284.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But one of the cruel ones which I had to not participate, fortunately-- I wouldn't be here-- had to witness was they thought it was very funny to take prisoners, send them around-- stand around the circle, and have one prisoner selected to have a bowel movement in the middle of these people.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And most human beings cannot do this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so the game was to force you to do something that's instinctual or reflex-wise not easy, and your life depended on it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, those are the few things that-- I mean, the cruelty was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But actual activity was none.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You just wait for your fate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had been there for a little bit more than two months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the rule that everybody sort of assumed was that you don't ever volunteer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was strange.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was in the latrine, which in itself is ridiculous because with one thin slice of bread and a little bit of stew, you had very little reason to go using the toilet facilities.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Somebody comes in, and they're looking for volunteers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "No way in the world will I ever understand what made me jump up, run to the place where they're making a selection, and not only volunteer, but I raised my arms, and I speak German.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I speak German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No idea.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The German officer that made the selection understood and said, OK.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were 131 juveniles, exclusively juveniles, that were now taken to a barrack, and now we were given a number.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was no need for a number to be given when you go in because the extermination camp isn't interested in numbering you to be killed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They need to give you a number, they felt, in case you might escape.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, you looked like a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
